{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1326605, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260923, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "普通人，远离军事区及大型城市中心区。做好物资储备，尽量收集保值物品。社会秩序正常时，安心工作。", "timestamp": 1616604681, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326618, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260923, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不打到核战基本不会直接影响你的生活，最大的影响就是你可能会失业。\n即使是核战，非军事区，非大型城市中心区的人也有极大机会幸存，只是战后需要面对崩溃的社会秩序。", "timestamp": 1616604752, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326688, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 260923, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "根据我看的二战材料，战争一代会有非常严重的心理问题…", "timestamp": 1616605394, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326800, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 260923, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不要哇carol受不了那种生活(°ー°〃)", "timestamp": 1616606497, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326807, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 260923, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那北京会是最安全的还是最危险的?", "timestamp": 1616606564, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1326895, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 260923, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 军事风险高，社会风险低\n导弹炸弹优先朝你招呼，但走路上被失业人员捅死的风险较低（社会秩序优先报账）", "timestamp": 1616607514, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 260923, "reply": 6, "tag": null, "text": "如果有一天战争真的来了，该怎么办呢", "timestamp": 1616604592, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1616607514, "url": "", "vote": {}}}